title: Cuties: PED*BAIT or Art Film? A Review

media:group.media:title: Cuties: PED*BAIT or Art Film? A Review
media:group.media:description:
Cuties, is it a movie aimed at those individuals attracted to underage girls or is it a misunderstood art film that's really a critique of society pushing sexualization onto young children? 

Like most thing I thought I would just bang out a low effort rant but as I started working on it, things becomes more and more involved.

Seems like because of the subject matter Youtube auto turned off comments. Hopefully they're back on.
